Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here's my new weapon, Kuwagata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you all set, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, but I only made this to look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how it will actually work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Aim for the \Ncenter of that lug's gut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Special Attack! Iron Man Comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not done yet, Oars.\NHe's still hanging on by a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That cloud...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did they do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit yelling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if he notices me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What? What?! Can he stretch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-His arm extended?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stretched. That feels \Nmore like how it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hat Crew Gets Wiped Out!\NThe Shadow-Shadow's Powers in Full Swing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the groove now that my body stretches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes another attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His attack power has skyrocketed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come Oars can stretch\Nwhen he isn't a power holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Moria do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good guess! I'm making you live this\Nnightmare with my Shadow-Shadow power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shadow Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Revolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadows copy whatever your body does.\NThat's common knowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body and shadow are always\Nmirror images of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a hard-and-fast rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars' shadow is supposed to obey him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I usurped control by\Nslipping my shadow inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can freely alter the shape of Oars' shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his shadow and body\Nmust take the same form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the shadow stops\Nmatching the shape of his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his body transforms to match his shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how Shadow Revolution works!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's the\Nopposite of common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria made the arms and legs\Nin Oars' shadow extend,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so his body stretched to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So instead of becoming a rubber man,\NOars' body can transform into anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break. He's too big for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I can't get near him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is far worse than rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make his shadow round...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars will turn into a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Just a sec, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep out of my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad! I didn't mean to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here to offer assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Oars! Crush each\Nand every one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where is Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria must have tricked him\Ninto going somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way he got his butt kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? I swear, he is such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Should I tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already in a tight spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there is another Warlord \Non this island right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So does this mean everyone\Nwon't get their shadows back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless we defeat both Zombie Luffy and Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's almost dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of the enemy's plan!\NWe just have to thwart it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Excuse me!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant me this one request!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get near him, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see what happened to Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me for what happens!\NThis packs a wallop, so get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloud Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! Please do your thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd use Kuwagata again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no greater pain than\Nbeing unable to repay a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall put in backbreaking effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slalom Vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The electricity is so strong\Nyou can see my bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was nothing but bones to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time! I'm like a lightning arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Bone Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gavotte Bond en Avant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! He drilled through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made an opening! Keep the attacks going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission: Complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style... Nigiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tower Climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you--no, first I'm going\Nto finish off that skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He wouldn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Atlas Comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crap!\N--Usopp, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fight"? Eh? Hey! Whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up next, Long Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My arm isn't stretching! Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochenta Fleurs Cuatro Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did these arms come from?!\NThey're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop manipulating\Nhis shadow for the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gak! C-Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this will \Nkeep me out of the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your plan doesn't amuse me in the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veinte Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calendula!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're \Ndoing to Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria's shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who is the more powerful\Nlong-distance power holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hold hurts pretty darn bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get distracted by his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take out his body,\Nthe shadow will disappear as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuatro Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sweet!\N--You're amazing, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin! Watch out\Nfor the shadow behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is Moria doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were close! It's such a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doppelman and I can switch\Nplaces at any given minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They switched places?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then the one inside Oars is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Shadow Substitute that\Nhas no joints to dislocate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It's the shadow that\Nwas here until just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's three down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's got Robin's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything to put it in,\Nbut I might as well take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Robin-chan's shadow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Haché!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He switched places with his shadow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he switched with his shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria is back inside Oars' stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything has returned to how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh darn it, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is supposed to be my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Oars. I had a bit\Ntoo much fun with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish off that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His arms can stretch out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! He's going to attack\NRobin when she's out cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Robin! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frit Assorti!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You repelled him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance!\NGet Robin-chan away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sanji! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, what are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching for what\Ncaused Oars to die 500 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after his right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't his real arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback reconstructed it, but there are signs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nof horrible frostbite around the stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say for certain, but I suspect\Nhe froze to death 500 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a monster like this is\Nno match for the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died while wandering the Land of Ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even 500 years ago,\NI'd wager Oars went around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mostly naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna lose to someone that stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies may not feel pain,\Nbut they still take damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the attacks we've\Nlanded are accumulating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can render this arm nonfunctional,\Nit will halve his offensive power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, focus on this one arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking up a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while standing on my shoulder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a zombie,\Nyou have no idea how badly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just hurt your own body\Nwith that punch, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, you went inside my fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! I'm tiny, so the crevices\Nin your fist are like caves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you dodged that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armée de l'Air...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cloven...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roseo Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hitting me in the same spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those attacks aren't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll work! Pain is a signal\Nmeant to protect the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lacking pain doesn't make you strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your fuzzy logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That looks bad, guys!\NGet away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're in for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There go another two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking everyone out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four down! Five down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea who you are,\Nbut thanks for rescuing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're stinking strong now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Incredible Battle \NStarts! Luffy vs. Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
